{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This-- this was called self-defense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was [INAUDIBLE] murder, but better them than us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen so many of us dying in the-- in the-- in the ghettos and so on, it was nice to see some of them dying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought it was-- I was doing a good job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a good feather boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the best there was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the best there was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- winters were cold, two of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the first, I grew out of my shoes so I had rags.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was bad to move all night because we're hidden in shallow trees, sometimes underground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In summer, it was good fun because I was taught to breathe like a fish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we'd lie in the water if there was any Germans or anybody around and the guards, so we'd get under the water and you would just leave you mouth up under a leaf.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You get a leaf, you hold the leaf and nothing-- just breath like a fish, quietly, quietly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just breathe like a fish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Ukrainian forests, you get lots of water, you know, in our boots-- but I'd get into not too deep so I wouldn't drown, of course.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't swim then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were just-- under water there's lots of this, lots of water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were pretty excited because they would get bogged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, the Germans didn't want to get in the water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't go by car or motorcycle or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if they went there, that's when they got their-- their-- their throat cut.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they got lost, this is the way they got killed in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we did a bit of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
